<item>
            <title>[CXF-3931] STS SAMLTokenValidator doesn&apos;t validate condition</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-3931</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The SAMLTokenValidator doesn&apos;t verify whether the condition in the SAML token meets the current time.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
